data.description: Gorgeous home on 2 acres in Honeysuckle Estates! 3bdr, 2bath, 2.5gar. 30x60 dream workshop with 20 ft porch for your collections or tractor with electric and Hot tub. Remodeled kitchen and master bath and large bedrooms. Wood blinds throughout. Hidden extras galore including upgraded windows and high efficiency 18 seer AC. Office space with garage access. Inside city limits with over 40 mature trees and a retreat feel. This home is truly a must see!
